'''Jorge Garcia''' (2188 - 2222) was an American actor. He was the son actress [[Desiree Garcia]], grandson of art gallery professional [[Lynn Garcia]], great-grandson of magician [[Odell Garcia]], great-great-grandson of businessman [[Eduardo Garcia]], great-great-great-grandson of baseball player [[Colt Garcia]], and great-great-great-great-grandson of musician [[Donald Garcia]]. 

